OL,3,GNEWSC"All areas of BBC News" to be
OL,4,Caffected by cost-cutting: BBC News CEO
OL,5,
OL,6,FBBC News Interim CEO Jonathan Munro has
OL,7,Fwritten to staff confirming that all
OL,8,Fareas of BBC News will be affected by
OL,9,Fcost-cutting measures.
OL,11,FThe statement follows a BBC-wide
OL,12,Fannouncement yesterday of a target to
OL,13,Fsave around #500 million over the next
OL,14,Ftwo years, with most savings required
OL,15,Fwithin the next financial year.
OL,17,FThe BBC expects to lose 1,800 ` 2,000
OL,18,Froles across the organisation. Munro
OL,19,Fcites rising production and technology
OL,20,Fcosts, declining licence fee income,
OL,21,Fand challenges in commercial markets as
OL,22,Fthe drivers.
OL,23,EPub: 16-Apr-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,147,140,200,120,0,100
