OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F146A1777206669
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/3
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNEWSC"All areas of BBC News" to be
OL,4,Caffected by cost-cutting: BBC News CEO
OL,5,
OL,6,FFurther detail on how savings will be
OL,7,Fachieved in News is expected to be
OL,8,Fshared in June, though Munro warns this
OL,9,Fwill likely represent only part of the
OL,10,Ffull picture of changes to come.
OL,12,FA Voluntary Redundancy (VR) window will
OL,13,Fbe opened in the coming months, with
OL,14,Fthe BBC aiming to make changes through
OL,15,FVR rather than compulsory redundancy
OL,16,Fwherever possible.
OL,23,EPub: 16-Apr-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
