OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F146A1777206669
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/3
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNEWSC"All areas of BBC News" to be
OL,4,Caffected by cost-cutting: BBC News CEO
OL,5,
OL,6,FMunro acknowledges that the BBC will
OL,7,Fnot be able to retain everything it
OL,8,Fcurrently broadcasts, with linear
OL,9,Faudiences in decline, while pledging to
OL,10,Fboost BBC News on digital platforms `
OL,11,Fparticularly for younger audiences.
OL,13,FImmediate cost control measures already
OL,14,Fin place include restrictions on
OL,15,Ftravel, conferences, events, awards and
OL,16,Fnon-essential recruitment.
OL,18,FDespite the cuts, Munro insists the
OL,19,FBBC's commitment to "outstanding,
OL,20,Fimpartial and original journalism"
OL,21,Fremains unchanged.
OL,23,EPub: 16-Apr-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
